title: Time Team - Season 09 (2002) - 13 Episodes
description:
Time Team - Season 09 (2002) - 13 Episodes

Season Summary:

The 2002 series saw Time Team investigating the Bronze-Age remains of what might have been London's first bridge, diving for a Spanish Armada shipwreck and finding early traces of the Industrial Revolution beneath a Shropshire pub.

Episode    Title
=======  ====================================================
  01     London's First Bridge, Vauxhall
  02     The Romans Panic, Lincolnshire
  03     Diving for the Armada, Kinlochbervie
  04     The Naughty Monastery, Chicksands
  05     The Furnace in the Cellar, Ironbridge
  06     An Ermine Street Pub, Cheshunt
  07     Iron-Age Market, Helford
  08     Siege House in Shropshire
  09     A Prehistoric Airfield, Throckmorton
  10     A Lost Roman City, Castleford
  11     Every Castle Needs a Lord, Warwickshire
  12     Steptoe et Filius, Isle of Wight
  13     Seven Buckets and a Buckle, Breamore, Hampshire
